  "extraHighlightWords": [],
  "sentences": [
    {
      "en": "Friday is officially family movie night, though tonight's plan quietly turned into something else entirely.",
      "zh": "星期五正式是我們家的電影夜，不過今晚的計畫悄悄變成了完全不同的東西。"
    },
    {
      "en": "We turned on the television expecting a normal film, but Dad accidentally clicked on a museum documentary program instead.",
      "zh": "我們打開電視原本是想看普通電影，結果爸爸不小心點到一個博物館紀錄片節目。"
    },
